snippet.title: No. 31 - Improv and Archer with Amber Nash
snippet.description:
Originally released Dec. 20, 2016 -  Amber Nash (Pam from the F/X series, Archer, improviser at ATL's Dad's Garage) is wonderfully talented and an all-around great person! ​Jason and Amber have a stellar and cheerful talk about how Amber got her start, learning and performing improv at the famed Atlanta Theater, Dad's Garage, and of course, how she got her role on Archer. It's a great and informative talk for improvisers and actors seeking work in the business! Take this delightful chat in and learn plenty while you're at it!

http://www.howtoruintheholidaysmovie.com
http://www.hartofamerica.com
https://dadsgarage.com
